ting about some "recovery amino acid complex" on the internet, I would've laughed at you.</p></span></div><div data-rid="30ac085c-9fd8-4ec8-be1e-dac01383c8d1" class="r-ol0due alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>But here's the thing...</p></span></div><div data-rid="8e382076-20cb-48df-a01d-10040fc82266" class="r-1h96gdb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>This shit's legit.</strong></p></span></div><div data-rid="880ca3cc-b5d5-44da-a4f1-71936f7e1e6b" class="r-vkupu2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>And if you told me six months ago that I'd be writing about some "recovery amino acid complex" on the internet, I would've laughed at you.</p></span></div><div data-rid="551b8a1b-e7f8-4145-a354-5df00dd762e8" class="r-uy4i4z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Being distracted and unfocused is not something to shrug off. It can jeopardize people’s ability to hit their work targets and put them at risk of blowing their chances of a promotion. Even worse, it can mean losing out to coworkers who <span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"><strong>can stay focused and get stuff done.</strong></span></p></span></div><div data-rid="b900e2ef-efe1-4c07-8fc3-48730b655626" class="r-1e1mr50 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong>While some people waste hours scrolling endlessly through Instagram, others are finding ways to</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"> <strong>hack their brains to achieve optimal productivity,</strong></span> almost at will.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="609e8610-e504-4959-bfca-d40eaeb3790b" class="r-1118jo1"><picture data-rid="4e693c20-4333-407f-b859-349ca8945d7f" class="r-voxcd7"><img src="https://andytown-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/templates/component-templates/Onnit-advert.json/63eb24ccca797b5c099f0c98_about15.jpg%3Fv%3D1678393304" class="r-lkuayi" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="74ceb05e-b1b2-436f-addb-dc56ee2eb7a6" class="r-10jbq24"><div data-rid="b5f74fbb-13e5-4b7b-8511-ff9b907e3a11" class="r-12yf85i"></div><div data-rid="c075f626-c3f6-4d3a-b1c5-19e2deca5a3f" class="r-nn3iwi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>An Easier Way of Attaining Flow States</p></span></div><div data-rid="539156f2-cc33-4610-846c-751ddafae178" class="r-1sgtfq6"></div></div><div data-rid="b62a127d-bcc7-4271-85be-b3ed48abb218" class="r-op3o8w"><div data-rid="8d76bad0-93c1-4edb-832a-556688861177" class="r-1i5ph2e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I'm not some guru trying to sell you on remarkable promotes wellness. I'm a 38-year-old former college wrestler who runs a construction company. I lift weights, I work with my hands, and my body takes a beating.</p></span></div><div data-rid="6065eea3-2f90-48fd-8730-f5eff82a05ca" class="r-1pgsvlq"><div class="r-u2cghl"><video src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/dfad0de1-d0c4-4519-8bfa-03ad392ab394/0efbc86a-a7fa-475b-9b7e-f42da5cf13bb" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="metadata" autoplay="" muted="" loop=""></video></div><div data-rid="0baf8314-9d4b-4706-b986-ff88a356c1e1" class="r-mo7r7s"><div data-rid="7cc3b6e0-eb5b-4d6d-8fd7-8ccd8e6db138" class="r-1oci8lh"><div data-rid="acbbc388-0585-4712-867c-1b038e33760e" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-192u3am"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation" aria-label="Pause" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-xwnncn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M5.5 3.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 7 5v6a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0V5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5-1.5m5 0A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 12 5v6a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0V5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5-1.5"></path></svg></div></div><div data-rid="22a4dc1c-b128-4197-99d7-9e07db0eca6c" class="r-1mo01jk"><div data-rid="7de6f1c8-a96b-426c-a008-bc350c056586" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-6jivc0"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 