="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"><strong>achieve a flow state</strong></span>, the brain needs to be at the right frequency. This frequency is when ‘alpha waves’ appear.</p></span></div><div data-rid="cad62218-506f-4e2f-a9d8-8ea445010e06" class="r-1nws2mo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>As reported in Psychology Today, neuroscientists have found alpha waves help to<span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"><strong> support creativity and concentration.</strong></span> Until recently, the only way to trigger alpha waves was through sending electrical pulses through the brain or deep meditation.</p></span></div><div data-rid="4829e0af-bc73-4add-a5db-8dd8b353d89e" class="r-14217yt"><div data-rid="944941d3-faf3-43af-aee5-758d3ead88fd" class="r-n7kufq"><div data-rid="36700765-9624-408c-a1db-63b988e1c6a3" class="r-11yxlfb"><div class="r-ucoeda"><video src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/2b4cdd289f134a21b6736c80063f2c32.mp4" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="auto" autoplay="" muted="" loop=""></video></div><div data-rid="46f8945a-133c-4a13-af24-4d611f2460f0" class="r-4u2nad"></div></div></div><div data-rid="bdfc8217-a14e-4179-9c92-839dfe98be22" class="r-16bphr8"><div data-rid="51a654f0-1224-457d-98ca-c87a76b1fd3a" class="r-zwmj2l"><div class="r-1ctwh5m"><video src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/797f8415c7474db2b34fcc37ce01bb25.mp4" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="metadata" muted=""></video></div><div data-rid="cf189c36-87ef-42d9-bb10-8326f252e371" class="r-3fyp0o"></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4aec9b22-67b8-440b-b9e1-e110e28793a5" class="r-np15y7"><div class="r-1p0hi07"><video src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/dfad0de1-d0c4-4519-8bfa-03ad392ab394/fb49d8e2-9272-46c7-a7ad-46fad57cc42c" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="auto" autop